// ---------------------------------------------------------------------
// SCUMGrid : SCUMContainer
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------
//
// container view that lays out child views in a tabular manner,
// either columns first or rows first.
//
// see also: SCUMContainer, SCUMHGrid, SCUMVGrid
//
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------
// properties
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------
//
// <> homogenous -- Boolean
//
//    when true, all child views will be assigned the same size.
//
// <> xSpacing -- Float
// <> ySpacing -- Float
//
//    amount of spacing added between child views in x and y direction.
//
// <> wrap -- Integer
//
//    wrap row or column. when adding views subclasses start a new
//    row/column when the wrap width has been reached.
//
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------
